{"tid":2034030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"1949上海 vs 2020香港","createTime":"2020-05-25T04:10:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T04:37:07.000Z","uid":73573,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d9a14b2e259f4be00677594d022fe8bd5429a5af","tid":2034030,"uid":73573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:10:33.000Z","msg":"回顧歷史，諷刺地何期相似<br />\n中國係共產黨統治下完全冇進步過<br />\n<br />\n1949年及之前上海，當時亞洲第一金融中心，規模比香港更大，各租界臨立。然而：<br />\n<br />\n「上海戰役，亦稱淞滬戰役，是1949年5月12日至27日間，中國人民解放軍與中華民國國軍在上海及周邊地區進行的戰役。解放軍快速獲勝，攻佔中國的經濟中心和最大、最重要的工業城市&mdash;&mdash;上海。中華民國政府稱上海淪陷，中國共產黨及中華人民共和國政府官方稱上海解放。」<br />\n<br />\n之後土改同三反五反，國進民退，連公私合營官督商辦都唔扮，所有工業成果同金融資產被共產黨沒收，上海每日上百個空降兵（破產/受迫害資本家跳樓），直到今日都翻唔到身。<br />\n<br />\n2020年5月27日爾後，香港將會被解放，今次唔係用軍隊，係共式法治同國家機械配合無產階級專政鐵拳，大家做好準備未？"},{"pid":"7c12048da66e0c321d3a07eab3a2f6c395a2f303","tid":2034030,"uid":73573,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:11:28.000Z","msg":"5月27日 被詛咒既日子"},{"pid":"2be8cc3ce6eb01bffb2dbc34c94f8bb8d39021a9","tid":2034030,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:11:34.000Z","msg":"攬炒啦柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d9d80d9a7ce5887b4987b4553c9f595e6d1fd14","tid":2034030,"uid":73573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:13:05.000Z","msg":"事隔71年後，慘況仍瀝瀝在目未敢忘"},{"pid":"556e91f2b405e610c4dcad7667cacae4053298f6","tid":2034030,"uid":119895,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:14:52.000Z","msg":"唐英年忘記左佢老豆點解要走佬黎香港"},{"pid":"a52ccaed94fb2fdbf5327288289afbe6b8b5fee5","tid":2034030,"uid":222140,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"556e91f2b405e610c4dcad7667cacae4053298f6","tid":2034030,"uid":119895,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:14:52.000Z","msg":"唐英年忘記左佢老豆點解要走佬黎香港"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:16:16.000Z","msg":"數典忘宗"},{"pid":"1f1be0be0a9e550d34d0072b6f1d278de153ebf5","tid":2034030,"uid":73573,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:16:18.000Z","msg":"大家儘快轉美金 走資<br />\n港紙會好似1949年法幣/金圓劵咁暴跌做牆紙<br />\n<br />\n全民加入香港無產階級行列，響應馬列史毛既共產革命"},{"pid":"710224a9e7f7b39f424d7ea08432174040df0411","tid":2034030,"uid":73573,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"556e91f2b405e610c4dcad7667cacae4053298f6","tid":2034030,"uid":119895,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:14:52.000Z","msg":"唐英年忘記左佢老豆點解要走佬黎香港"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:17:55.000Z","msg":"今日依個不孝子仲帶頭支持國安法<br />\n佢老豆應該欲哭無淚<br />\n唐家續命燈71年後正式油盡燈枯"},{"pid":"ce1e67bbf68a502f9da9baf668ad0e2a4113b76d","tid":2034030,"uid":73573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:19:07.000Z","msg":"沒有共產党就沒有新香港"},{"pid":"df1b104030e3ff68971681e6cbb8b5c7d9a8b9ef","tid":2034030,"uid":51820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"556e91f2b405e610c4dcad7667cacae4053298f6","tid":2034030,"uid":119895,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:14:52.000Z","msg":"唐英年忘記左佢老豆點解要走佬黎香港"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:19:45.000Z","msg":"今次中共保佢 唔驚 老豆咩黎嫁？食得嫁？"},{"pid":"56a481738ce020a1780fde879eecdc33650e5b7b","tid":2034030,"uid":242743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df1b104030e3ff68971681e6cbb8b5c7d9a8b9ef","tid":2034030,"uid":51820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"556e91f2b405e610c4dcad7667cacae4053298f6","tid":2034030,"uid":119895,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:14:52.000Z","msg":"唐英年忘記左佢老豆點解要走佬黎香港"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:19:45.000Z","msg":"今次中共保佢 唔驚 老豆咩黎嫁？食得嫁？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:20:37.000Z","msg":"狡兔死"},{"pid":"1fd9d357d0ee423c802b6b392021165bdcedee47","tid":2034030,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:21:29.000Z","msg":"中共咪笠水<br />\n藍屍咪走資<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\